The evidence with the title 'Global extreme poverty - our World In Data ' says Accordingly, the share of people in extreme poverty has decreased continuously over the course of the last two centuries .  ... . In 32 years, the share of people living in extreme poverty was divided by 4 , reaching levels below 11% in 2013.  ... The number of extremely poor people in the world is 3 times lower than in 1970 . 
